<section>
  <h2>Origins and Early Years</h2>
  <p>The Detroit Pistons were founded in 1941 as the Fort Wayne Zollner Pistons. They played in the Basketball Association of America, which would later become the NBA.</p>
  <h2>Championship Success</h2>
  <p>The Pistons' championship success peaked in the 1980s with the famous "Bad Boys" teams and then in the early 2000s with the "Pistons' 2004 Championship".</p>
